default)(
defaulta), 27(2)(a), 47(1)(b), 48(1).
default2.1.2
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultLeasehold Reform, Housing and Urban Development Act 1993, in 13(3)(f), 15(5)(a), 15(5)(b)(iii), 15(7)(a), 16(3)(c), 16(5)(c), 21(6), [22(2)(a)], 42(3)(e), 45(4), 99(2), 99(2)(b), 99(3). 
default2.1.3
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultLandlord and Tenant (Covenants) Act 1995, Section 27(2
default)(
defaultc).
default&#xa0;
default2.2
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIn Sub-section 47(1) of the Landlord and Tenant Act 1987, change the wording to:
default“(1)
default              
defaultWhere any written demand is given to a tenant of premises to which this part applies, the demand must contain an address in the United Kingdom at which notices (including notices in proceedings) may be served on the Landlord by the tenant.
